This paper deals with confidentiality enforcement in ontologies, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The Controlled Query Evaluation framework is a security mechanism, which is also related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions Datalog and OWL 2 profiles, which are ontology languages, and ontology is a topic related to logic (cs.LO) and software engineering (cs.SE).
